		<Card
			title='Design outside the box'
			image='design.jpg'
			imageAlt='A robot eating brushs and pencils. Sketch in the style of Leonardo da Vinci.'
			textAlt='This course is for web designers and web developers. They learn how to create innovative and impressive web designs that really stick with the help of AI. In the course they will learn how to use this super power to use unique AI-generated illustrations and images to create innovative and eye-catching web designs.'
			bgColor='bg-[#D66154]'
		>
			<p>
				If you want to design an amazing website, don't just settle for
				what you've seen everyone else do.
			</p>
			<p>
				Dive into new techniques based on A.I. that will make your site
