			</p>
		</Card>
		<Card
			title='Tap into untouched creative potential'
			image='copy.jpg'
			imageAlt='A robot eats a blue typewriter. Sketch in style of Leonardo da Vinci.'
			textAlt='This course is for web designers, web developers and copy writers. In the course they learn how to create copy texts that really stick with the help of AI. They will learn how to get great copy even with lacking creativity.'
