			imageAlt='A green robot sits in front of computer and thinks about programming code. Old sketch in style of Leonardo da Vinci.'
			textAlt='A course for web designers, web developers. They learn how to programme website code or create even complete websites with the help of AI.'
			bgColor='bg-[#758242]'
		>
			<p>
				So there are a lot of frameworks and engines out there that can
				help you code really fast, but is your business model for quick
				development, or a sophisticated and dynamic one?
			</p><p>
